// T036: `nsl-fmt --stdin` on a tiny `module foo {}` input.
// At T2 Phase 3a-CLI the formatter is still byte-passthrough
// (Phase 3 wires the LayoutPlanner) — output equals input.

// RUN: printf 'module foo {}\n' | nsl-fmt --stdin | FileCheck %s
// CHECK: module foo {}
